{"tid":1477080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先去左觀塘渣打","createTime":"2019-08-16T04:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T06:17:14.000Z","uid":7381,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b614d0228a50a9a0fcdb768b1e4f289ef52e4d9f","tid":1477080,"uid":7381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"小弟其實都係一個普通打工仔<br />\n今日放假咪諗住去渣打拎下錢洗下<br />\n其實我都唔係話拎好多錢<br />\n諗住拎八十幾萬返屋企數下銀紙咁啦<br />\n點知！<br />\n排到我喇<br />\n竟然叫我拎住一半先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWa咁大間銀行竟然連80萬都拎唔到<br />\n叫一眾打工仔點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩佢都應承我 下晝返去有得拎<br />\n如果冇得拎 大家話點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你地嘅錢都係放係渣打嘅<br />\n不如去問下有冇得拎啦<br />\n問下好喇 唔好拎晒出黎呀<br />\n銀行冇錢 擠提 好大鑊架！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：光復香港 光代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nI have no stake in the society <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18b073e5aeee2aa16c3768372434c52ca849943","tid":1477080,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19eed7549a34b71cf3919156d7058f39956bf12","tid":1477080,"uid":42541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:22:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0b2e0bdd7bb5a6c4064b225e1d8c6d6dc08f48e","tid":1477080,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"滙豐櫃員機無cash , 銀行班仆街點做野"},{"pid":"54ed75feb5b46c1a75386ecb7725b708f